==Latin==
===Conjunction===
'''ut''' ''+ subjunctive''

# [[that]], [[so that]], in order to, in order that
#: "Spero ut pacem habeant semper." - ''"I hope that they may always have peace."''

'''ut''' ''+ indicative''
# [[as]], [[just as]]

